{"id":6834,"date":"2023-11-05T20:20:30","date_gmt":"2023-11-05T12:20:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/?page_id=6834"},"modified":"2023-11-05T21:12:55","modified_gmt":"2023-11-05T13:12:55","slug":"trade-supply-chain-management","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/services\/trade-supply-chain-management\/","title":{"rendered":"Trade and supply chain services for Greater China"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1>Trade &amp; supply chain management services for Greater China<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h1>\n<div>\n<p>Successfully source from or sell to China with Acclime\u2019s local expertise.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"\/contact\/\">Talk to an expert<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"#more\">Learn more<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime_web_image_10.jpg\" alt=\"Trade &#038; supply chain management services for Greater China\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime-dots-grid.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Outsource your China trade operations &amp;&nbsp;sourcing<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>China&rsquo;s market potential is immense but hard to harness. B2B and B2C companies can unlock profitability in the region by leveraging our local trade and supply chain resources. Whether you need sales and distribution, sourcing, merchandising, or purchasing, our end-to-end services are designed to meet your needs at each stage of your China business.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/attention.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Regional resources<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>Connect with our regional network of reliable partners and service providers, including e-commerce partners, warehousing and logistics experts, import agents, and customs consultants.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/dedicated-staff.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Multi-industry expertise<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>Through our extensive client work, we have accumulated deep know-how in clusters as diverse as medical devices, F&#038;B, machinery parts, toys, furniture, DIY products, and sporting goods.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/compliance-services.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Digitally-driven efficiency<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>ERP, CRM, and other software solutions optimise your supply chain management by streamlining communication, structuring workflow, automating processes, and improving data quality.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>A lack of local expertise is no barrier to pursuing opportunities in China<span style=\"color: #FF8200;\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re sourcing from or selling to Greater China, running an efficient local supply chain requires on-site presence and on-time action. Acclime&rsquo;s cross-location China team acts on your behalf to plan and execute your sourcing and distribution operations when you lack the local resources.<\/p>\n<p>Your team will include highly specialised import\/export consultants, project managers, merchandisers, and logistics and documentation specialists who guarantee a timely and hassle-free journey for your products.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg);\"><\/span> Import, sales and distribution services<\/h6>\n<h2>Trade operations management &amp; sourcing services<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"> <\/span> Selling to China<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li><strong>Advice<\/strong> on distribution structure and online\/offline S&amp;D channels&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Product registration<\/strong> support &ndash; CCC, CFDA&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Customs advisory<\/strong> for China import regulations, special trade zones, duty optimisation, product labels and certificates&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Import operations:<\/strong> customs clearance, local deliveries, billing, specialized imports&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Order and inventory management<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Customer\/distributor services<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"> <\/span> Merchandising services<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li><strong>Managing product development projects<\/strong> from product concept and design rendering, to prototyping, sampling, and mass production\u00a0<\/li>\n<li><strong>Ensuring vendors compliance<\/strong> with importing country regulations (CE, REACH, BSCI, FSC)\u00a0<\/li>\n<li><strong>Executing factory audits<\/strong>\u00a0<\/li>\n<li><strong>Coordinating inspection and product testing<\/strong> to meet regulations in individual markets\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/circle.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"> <\/span> Sourcing from China<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li><strong>Supporting client strategies<\/strong> via product scouting&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Feasibility assessments<\/strong> for sourcing project&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Researching and qualifying new<\/strong> vendors according to the client&rsquo;s requirements&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Organising buying trips and trade fairs visits<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"uk-margin-small-bottom\"><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg'); margin-bottom: 4px; width: 16px;\"> <\/span> Purchasing operations<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-small-top\">\n<li><strong>OTC (order-to-cash) operations<\/strong>: order management, credit control, schedule monitoring, logistics coordination, invoicing, payment and collection\u00a0<\/li>\n<li><strong>Vendor collaboration<\/strong> to optimise costs, reduce lead time, improve quality, and ensure reliability<\/li>\n<li><strong>SOPs and system requirements<\/strong> for EU and North American buyers<\/li>\n<li><strong>Trade finance<\/strong> handling \u2013 L\/C, D\/P, D\/A, factoring solutions<\/li>\n<li><strong>Value-add services<\/strong> \u2013warehousing, shipment consolidation, vendor due diligence, scorecards, and contract reviews<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url('\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg');\"><\/span> <span style=\"color: #00263e;\">Tecnology-enabled professional services<\/span><\/h6>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #00263e;\">Streamline your operations with customised trade and supply chain technology solutions<\/span><span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime-line-graphic-1.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<p>Your trade activities will be supported by our unique enterprise resource planning (ERP) digital capabilities. <a href=\"\/services\/microsoft-dynamics-erp-crm-solutions\/\">Enterprise solutions<\/a> integrates your entire\u202f<strong>order-to-cash process<\/strong>\u202f\u2013 sales, purchasing, inventory, logistics, invoicing, and payment \u2013 into a single online platform giving you full visibility and control over the workflows we manage. Customisation allows you to dictate the design of the platform according to the requirements of your headquarters and local subsidiaries.<\/p>\n<p>The enterprise solutions platform connects to a range of external systems, and our in-house application team is experienced at developing interfaces with SAP, Dynamics NAV, Dynamics AX, Web-based ordering systems, 3PL, and cloud-based systems. The end result for your operations are increased speed and enhanced collaboration among different parties involved in the supply chain.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h5>Ready to get started?<\/h5>\n<h2>Discover how we can provide tech-enabled solutions to your trade &amp; supply needs in Greater China<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"\/contact\/\">Talk to an expert<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><br \/>\n<!-- {\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"animation\":\"fade\",\"css\":\".el-section {\\n    background-image: linear-gradient(to top,#f9f9f9,transparent);\\n}\",\"image\":\"wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/dotted-grid-medium.svg\",\"image_effect\":\"parallax\",\"image_height\":\"300\",\"image_parallax_bgx\":\"-300,-300\",\"image_position\":\"center-left\",\"media_visibility\":\"xl\",\"padding\":\"large\",\"style\":\"default\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"width\":\"default\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"props\":{\"layout\":\"2-3,1-3\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"width_medium\":\"2-3\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"breadcrumbs\",\"props\":{\"show_current\":false,\"show_home\":true}},{\"type\":\"headline\",\"props\":{\"content\":\"Trade &amp; supply chain management services for Greater China<span class=\\\"acc-orange\\\">.<\\\/span>\",\"margin\":\"default\",\"title_element\":\"h1\"}},{\"type\":\"text\",